💳 Financial Fraud Detection & Analytics Platform
📌 Overview

This project is an end-to-end fraud detection system that uses data analytics and machine learning to identify suspicious financial transactions and detect fraud patterns.

The system analyzes transaction behavior such as spending patterns, transaction velocity, device changes, and geographic anomalies to generate risk scores and fraud alerts.

🎯 Objectives
Detect fraudulent transactions using machine learning
Identify risk levels (Normal, Medium Risk, Fraud Alert)
Analyze transaction behavior patterns
Provide real-time fraud monitoring
Build an interactive dashboard and web application
🧠 Key Features
📊 Fraud prediction using ML model
⚠ Risk scoring system
🔍 Behavioral anomaly detection
📈 Power BI dashboard for analytics
🌐 Streamlit web app for real-time detection
📥 CSV upload & fraud report download
