⚡ Risk Scoring System

Risk score is calculated using behavioral indicators:

risk_score = (
    velocity_score * 0.3 +
    spending_deviation_score * 0.3 +
    geo_anomaly_score * 0.4
) * 100
Risk Levels
✅ Normal (0–40)
⚠ Medium Risk (40–70)
🚨 Fraud Alert (70+)
🔥 Advanced Features (Level 2)
Rolling window transaction analysis
